&lt;p&gt;Karloff company is the producer and distributor of the&nbsp;very popular Slovak alcoholic beverages Tatransky caj (Tatra tea). When you visit the High Tatras and their &ldquo;outlaw Tatra chalets,&rdquo; you will be offered as an aperitif the local specialty: hot tea made from Tatra herbs soaked in concentrated alcohol. For many years, we had been thinking about the idea of bringing this specialty to every home and business in Slovakia as a consumer product. Karloff create a substance of quality, there is no haste involved. The longer it takes to prepare things, the higher the achieved quality will be; the products are finer, more subtle and riper, just like good wine and old cognac. What do their products have in common? Moments you enjoy with your loved ones. Moments of joy, happiness, indulgence, understanding, grief and gratefulness.&lt;/p&gt;
